   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>"Papontos, alias Patas, foreman of the southern ousia, to Matreas the most honoured, greetings. If it seems right to you, lord, send me then for my outlays forty drachmas, total 40 drachmas, of which I shall render an account, through the medium of Psenanubis. (2nd hd.) I wish you well. (3rd hd.) Year 23 of Antoninus Caesar the lord, the 22nd of the month Hadrianus. (4th hd.) Give the 40 drachmas."</ab>
         </div>
